reviewText: It has three separate videos and kept my child occupied for a big part of a long flight.
Title: Elmo's World Best of Elmo's World Two

reviewText: Elmo is a hit!!!  My Toddler is eating better now from watching Elmo, no joke!!  He is a picky eater, too and loves everything!!!
Title: Elmo's World Best of Elmo's World Two

reviewText: I ordered this box set for my 2yr old's 2nd Christmas. Now all she says is Elmo! She evens sings the theme song!! Its super cute to see her take a liking to something, it is really getting her to talk and interact more!!
Title: Elmo's World Best of Elmo's World Two

reviewText: It is a great set that I got for my Elmo loving infant.  With nine episodes of Elmo talking about mail, taking a bath, families, exercise, drinking water, what is in the sky, and more, it us educationally fun for those of all ages.
Title: Elmo's World Best of Elmo's World Two

reviewText: two years old daughter loved this set.  My son 4 1/2 who usually doesn't watch Elmo loves to sit and watch it too.  I like this set.  Other than this set we have "flower,banannas, and more" dvd of Elmo's World.  Kids like these dvds a lot.
Title: Elmo's World Best of Elmo's World Two

reviewText: My kids are Elmo fanatics, so they will love this DVD.  They stick to the same tried and true formula that has worked before, and it covers some nice learning topics for the kids.
Title: Elmo's World Best of Elmo's World Two
